long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
You're not an imposter, everyone else is just bragging.

Are you tired of scrolling through your LinkedIn feed past countless posts not-so-humbly bragging about achievements, new jobs, books published, companies acquired, and IPOs? 

One of the greatest contributors to imposter syndrome and depression is social comparison -- constantly comparing yourself to others' bests is not healthy. 

This extension helps you feel less like an imposter by making it abundantly clear which posts are HumbleBrags and which are not.

Note: You can also disagree with the HumbleBrag label and submit feedback to improve the detection algorithm.
